INSURANCE
Complete Vlocity Installation Assistant Steps

To complete the installation and configuration of Insurance do all tasks marked New Installation Only and all unmarked tasks.

If installing in a Government Cloud org, disable Lock sessions to the IP address from which they originated setting prior to using the Vlocity Installation Assistant. To learn how to disable this setting, see Update Session Settings for the Insurance Installation in Government Cloud Orgs.

From the App Launcher, find and select Vlocity Installation Assistant.
Click the Assistant tab.
Click Reload Steps to see all configuration tasks.
Follow instructions to complete each task in the Assistant, or click Complete All or Complete Step for automatic or individual steps.
For manual tasks:
  Click Show Instructions
  Do the task in your Insurance org
  Go back and Mark Complete

After completing all steps, uninstall the Vlocity Installation Assistant. See Uninstall the Vlocity Installation Assistant.

To automatically add core picklist values to a Government Cloud org using the Installation Assistant, you must disable the Lock sessions to the IP address from which they originated setting.
Let us know if this article solved your issue!
title: Completing Vlocity Insurance Installation
